==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hazardous
<hw>Haz"ard*ous</hw> <pr>(-⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>hasardeux</ets>.]</ety> <def>Exposed to hazard; dangerous;
risky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To enterprise so <qex>hazardous</qex> and high!</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Perilous; dangerous; bold; daring; adventurous;
venturesome; precarious; uncertain.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Haz"ard*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Haz"ard*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>hazardousness</ent>⟦br⟧
